    "**Formal Psychiatric/Psychological Evaluation:** A comprehensive evaluation by a psychiatrist or clinical psychologist is crucial. This will help optimize management of his existing anxiety disorder, explore the role of his high-stress job, and provide specific strategies for panic attack management, potentially including medication adjustments or advanced CBT techniques.",
